summary_one_paragraph: This secret dispatch addresses concerns about Barry [CYFRAIL/L (201-845063) and the possibility of sensitive information being compromised through [CYFRAIL/1. It reports that [CYFRAIL/1 is residing in Pottstown, Pennsylvania, and seeks employment with R.C.A. in a classified Caribbean project. During their ten and one-half months of association, [CYFRAIL/1 was introduced to multiple WOFIRM personnel, including Drone Tenley, Richard Rice, and Frank Nagy. Furthermore, [CYFRAIL/1 was surveilled visiting IDEN A, an organization currently under investigation by the station.
title: RYBAT FJDUST - CJ MIL/1 - Damage Report
